data.name: Literal.Error.Address.DoubleConfirm

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.ID

data.comment: The error message for invalid apartment ID.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Insufficient

data.comment: The error message for insufficient information for address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.InvalidData
data.value: Aterese e e sa siamang, please siamisa aterese ya gago.
data.comment: The error message when data is missing for address verification.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Multiple
data.value: Aterese e e sa siamang, please siamisa aterese ya gago.
data.comment: The error message for invalid address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Pobox
data.value: Bokose ya PO ga e tshegediwe. Tsweetswee neela ka aterese ya gago.
data.comment: The error message for POBOX.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.PostalCode
data.value: Khoutu ya poso ga e bonwe. Tsweetswee siamisa aterese ya gago.
data.comment: The error message for invalid postal code.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Route
data.value: Sesupi sa tirelo ya routu ga se bonwe kgotsa se tswile tlhatlhamanong. Tsweetswee siamisa aterese ya gago.
data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Street
data.value: Leina la aterese ga le bonwe mo Khoutu ya poso e e totobaditsweng. Tsweetswee siamisa aterese ya gago.
data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail
data.value: Re ka se kgone go nayatetla mokgwa ono wa tuelo. Tsweetswee tlhomamisa gore tshedimosetso e siame, kgotsa dirisa mofuta o mongwe we tuelo. Fa o tswelela go bona molaetsa ono, tsweetswee ikgolaganye le setheo sa tsa madi.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail2
data.value: Go nnile le bothata ka go rurifadiwa ga sediriswa sa gago sa tuelo. Tsweetswee ikgolaganye le tirelo ya badirisi go bona thuso.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails. Probably, the PI is rejected by risk.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.BR
data.value: Ga re a kgona go letlelela pataganyotiragatso eno. Tsweetswee tlhomamisa tshedimosetso ya gago. Dikarata dingwe tsa go duela di ka nna tsa se amogelwe mo thulaganyong eno, mme fa go ntse jalo, re go kgothaletsa go dirisa karata e nngwe ya go duela. Fa bothata bo tswelela, o ka nna wa ikgolaganya le setheo sa gago sa tsa madi.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Brazil. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.MX
data.value: Ga re a kgona go letlelela pataganyotiragatso eno. Tsweetswee tlhomamisa tshedimosetso ya gago. Dikarata dingwe tsa go duela di ka nna tsa se amogelwe ke dithulaganyo tsa go duela ka ntlha ya dipholisi tse di gone tsa tshireletsego. Fa bothata bo tswelela, o ka nna wa ikgolaganya le setheo sa gago sa tsa madi.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Mexico. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.CardUsedMuiltipleTimes
data.value: Mokgwa wa gago wa tuelo o tsentswe go diakhaonto di le dintsi thata. Tsweetswee leka ka o mongwe.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card is used too many times.

data.name: Literal.Error.CcExpired
data.value: Karatamolato ya gago e feletswe ke nako. Tsweetswee tlhopha letlha la go felelwa ke nako la mo isagweng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the credit card is expired.

data.name: Literal.Error.CcNumberInvalid
data.value: Nomore ya karatamolato ya gago ga e a siama. Tsweetswee tsenya nomore ya karatamolato e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the credit card number is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdBankCodeInvalid
data.value: Nomore ya thomelo ya gago ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit bank code is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdBranchCodeInvalid
data.value: Khoutu ya go tlhaola ya gago ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit branch code is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdNumberInvalid
data.value: Nomore ya gago ya akhaonto ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit account number is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.AccountIdInvalid
data.value: Akhaonto ya gago ga e a siama.
data.comment: The error message is shown when the billable account id is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.AccountLocked
data.comment: The error message is shown when the billable account is locked or disabled.

data.name: Literal.Error.EnterValidInfo
data.value: Tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when user enters invalid information.

data.name: Literal.Error.EnterValidInfo2
data.value: Tshedimosetso ya mokgwa wa gago wa tuelo ga e a siama. Fa o tswelela o bona molaetsa ono, leka go dirisa mokgwa o mongwe wa tuelo kgotsa ikgolaganye le tirelo ya badirisi go bona thuso.
data.comment: The error message shown when user enters invalid information.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAddress
data.value: Aterese ya gago ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the address is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAddress2
data.value: Aterese ya gago ga e a siama. Tsweetswee tlhomamisa gore tshedimosetso ya gago ya aterese e siame.
data.comment: The error message shown when the address is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidCity
data.value: Toropo ya gago ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the city is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidPhoneType
data.value: Tshedimosetso ya founo ya gago ga e amogelesege, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e amogelesegang.
data.comment: The error message shown when the phone type is not valid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidState
data.value: Naga ya gago ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the state is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidZipcode
data.value: Khoutu ya zip ya gago ga e a siama, tsweetswee tsenya tshedimosetso e e siameng.
data.comment: The error message shown when the zipcode is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.PhoneNumberRequired
data.value: Nomore ya mogala e a tlhokega.
data.comment: The error message shown when the phone number is missing.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiAlreadyExists
data.value: Ga re kgone go tsenya mokgwa ono wa tuelo ka gonne o setse o le teng mo akhaontong ya gago. Tsweetswee leka ka o mongwe.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card that is already added.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiAlreadyExists2
data.value: Ga re kgone go tsenya mokgwa wa tuelo. Tsweetswee tlhomamisa gore ga o ise o tsenngwe go le pele go akhaonto ya gago. Fa o tswelela o amogela molaetsa ono, leka mokgwa o mongwe wa tuelo kgotsa ikgolaganye le tirelo ya badirisi go bona thuso.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card that is already added.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiBanned
data.value: Mokgwa wa gago wa tuelo o thibetswe. Tsweetswee leka ka o mongwe.
data.comment: The error message shown when the PI is banned.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiExceedMaxOwnership
data.value: Tshedimosetso e o neileng e dirisitswe ke diakhaonto di le dintsi thata. Tsweetswee tsenya akhaonto e nngwe kgotsa aterese ya imeile.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add a pi which has been used by other accounts for many times.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiLimitExceeded
data.value: Ga e kgone go tsenya seratwabogolo sa tuelo. Dirisa seratwabogolo sa tuelo se se leng teng, kgotsa go tlosa seratwabogolo sa tuelo.
data.comment: The error message shown when paper check last name is not correct.

data.name: Literal.Error.SaInIntermediateStatus

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.AR
data.value:
E le gore re go tlamele ka dikumo le ditirelo o tlhokiwa gore o tlhame akhaonto ya modirisi. Nako le nako fa o neelana ka sediriswa se se ntšhwa sa tuelo ya kumo kgotsa tirelo re ka nna ra go neela kitsiso e e latelang le go amogela tumalano ya gago pele ga o tswelela. Ka nako ya le ka mabaka a go tlhama akhaonto le/kgotsa go tsenya sediriswa se se ntšhwa sa tuelo o tla tlhokiwa gore o neelane ka tshedimosetso ya sebele e e jaaka: leina la gago, aterese, nomore ya mogala, aterese ya imeile, nomore ya karatamolato le nomore ya akhaonto ya banka. Gape re ka nna ra kgobokanya aterese ya gago ya IP le ID ya sediriswa sa gago le go amanya tshedimosetso eno le tshedimosetso ya sebele e o e neileng bakeng sa go tlhama akhaonto kgotsa fa o tsenya sediriswa se se ntšhwa sa tuelo.
Ke rebola ka mo go utlwalang gore Microsoft Corporation, bagwebimmogo le baemedi ba yone, ba dirise tshedimosetso ya sebele e ke e neileng fano, jaaka fa go tlhalositswe melawaneng ya Molao No. 25,326, Karolo 5 bakeng sa mabaka a go nthomelela dikgatiso le/kgotsa dilo tsa papatso malebana le dineelo tsa bone tsa dilwana le/kgotsa ditirelo. Ka gone ke bolela fano gore tumalanong le Molao No. 25,32, Section 6, ke ile ka itsisiwe kaga boithaopo jwa seno.
Go se neele tshedimosetso ga go reye matswela ape fela go na le go palelwa ke go bona tetlelesego go dikumo le ditirelo tse di neilweng mo setsheng seno sa webo. Fa nka neela tshedimosetso ya me, ke tla bo ke neela tumalano ya me ka mo go utlwalang le gore tshedimosetso e e ntseng jalo e bolokiwe mo databeiseng ya Microsoft Corporation e e kwa Redmond, WA 98052. Mong wa tshedimosetso ya sebele o na le tshwanelo ya go bona tetlelesego ya tshedimosetso e e ntseng jalo ka dikgaotso tse di ka se nneng bokhutshwane jwa kafa tlase ga dikgwedi di le thataro ntle le fa bosupi bo ka neelwa jwa kgatlhego e e utlwalang ya go dira dilo ka tsela e sele jaaka fa go bontshitswe ke Molao No. 25,326, Karolo 14, Karolo-potlana 3. Bothati jo bo nang le taolo ya go diragatsa Molao No. 25,326 ke ARGENTINE DIRECTORATE OF PERSONAL DATA PROTECTION mme ka go rialo e neilwe dithata tsa go berekana le ngongorego epe fela le/kgotsa tleleimi e e nnang gone ka ntlha ya go palelwa ke go latela dithulaganyo tse di laolang tshireletso ya tshedisetso ya sebele.
O ka nna wa bona tetlelesego kgotsa wa fetola tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele kwa: https://billing.microsoft.com. Fa go ka direga gore o tlhophe go fetola tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele ka go rialo o neela tumelelo e e letlang Microsoft Corporation go kgobokanya le go boloka tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele jaaka go tlhalositswe fa godimo.
Ka go tlhama akhaonto le go tobetsa konopo ya "Dumalana" e e fa tlase o dumalana go neela Microsoft Corporation tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele le go dumela gore Microsoft Corporation e e kgobokanye le go e fudusa jaaka fa go bontshitswe fano.
data.comment: Consent text for ES-AR

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.KR
data.value:
Tshedimosetso eno ya akhaonto e e supegang ya sebele e tla kokoanngwale go fudusiwa ka bonako fela morago ga go tlhamiwa ga akhaonto ka tsela e e babalesegileng, e e sireletsegileng go Microsoft Corporation kwa United States gore go diragadiwe dipataganyotiragatso tsa gago. Tshedimosetso eo e ka dirisiwa le go bolokiwa go fitlha go dingwaga di le lesomelebobedi go simolola ka tuelo ya gago ya bofelo. O ka ikgolaganya le Microsoft Corporation malebana le go laolwa ga tshedimosetso eno ya sebele e e supegang ka ikgolaganyo e e thathamisitsweng go Seteitemente sa Bosephiri sa Inthanete sa Microsoft se se fitlhelwang fano: http://privacy.microsoft.com/ko-kr.

Tshedimosetso ya gago e fetisediwa pele fa e le gore go dira jalo go tlhokega ka selekanyo se se tshwanelang go diragatsa pataganyotiragatso ya gago, go dumalana le tiragatso ya semolao, go tsibogela dingongorego, go thibela bonweenwee kgotsa go dira tumalanong le melawana ya puso.
O ka nna wa bona tetlelesego kgotsa wa fetola tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele kwa: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Fa go ka direga gore o tlhophe go fetola tshedimosetso ya gago go raya gore o neela tumelelo e e letlang Microsoft Corporation go kokoanya le go romela tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele ka bonako jaaka go tlhalositswe fa godimo.
Ka go tlhama akhaonto le go tobetsa konopo ya “Dumalana” e e fa tlase o dumalana go neela Microsoft Corporation tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele le go dumalana le Microsoft gore e kokoanye, e fuduse le go tlhakanela tshedimosetso ya gago ya sebele e e supegang le ditlamo tse dingwe jaaka go boletswe fano le go Polelwaneng ya Polokodiphiri ya Inthanete sa Microsoft e e fitlhelwang fano: http://privacy.microsoft.com/ko-kr

data.name: Literal.PICVC.Input.Inform
data.value: Pataganyotiragatso ya netefatso e lefisitswe go karatamolato ya gago. Tsweetswee lebelela seteitemente sa gago o bo o tsenya bokana kgo jo bo lefisiwang go akhaonto ya gago -KGOTSA- tsenya khoutu ya dinomore tse 3 e e fitlhelwang go tlhaloso ya pataganyotiragatso.
data.comment: Inform of input.

data.name: Literal.PICVC.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Re tla lefisa bokana jo bo sa utulolwang fa gare ga {0} {1} - {2} go tswa go karatamolato ya gago.
  • Bokana jo bo lefisiwang o tla bo busediwa ka bonako fela fa o fetsa tiragatso ya netefatso.
  • Gore o netefadiwe, o tshwanetse wa tsenya bokana kgo jo bo lefisiwang KGOTSA khoutu ya dinomore tse tharo e e neelwang mo tlhalosong ya pataganyotiragatso.
  • O ka bona bokana jo bo lefisitsweng kgotsa khoutu ya dinomore tsa 3 ka go tlhola seteitemente sa gago sa karatamolato. Go ikaegile ka Tirelo ya banka ya gago, seno se ka dirwa mo inthaneteng, ka mogala, kgotsa ka seteitemente sa pampiri se se tlang le imeile.
  • O tlhoka go feleletsa netefatso eno ka di {3}, mme o na le ditshono di le {4} tsa go leka gape.
  • Go ikaegile ka lefelo la gago le lefelo la banka e e neelanang ka karata ya gago, banka e ka nna ya lefisa Madi a Tuelo ya Bodit?habat?haba (ITF) kgotsa ya diragatsa ditefiso tsa phetolelo ya ledi go bokana jo bo lefisiwang ka nako ya tiragatso ya netefatso. Go tlhola gore a ditefiso tseo di ka dira, tsweetswee tlhola la banka e e neelanang ka karata. ITF kgotsa tefiso ya phetolelo ya ledi e e nnang teng mo tiragatsong ya netefatso ga e KITLA e busediwa madi ke Microsoft
data.comment: PICVC term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.name: Literal.PICVCDDPayin.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Re tla lefisa bokana jo bo sa utulolwang fa gare ga {0} {1} - {2} go tswa go akhaonto ya gago ya banka.
  • Bokana jo bo lefisiwang o tla bo busediwa ka bonako fela fa o fetsa tiragatso ya netefatso.
  • Gore o netefadiwe, o tshwanetse wa tsenya bokana kgo jo bo lefisiwang KGOTSA khoutu ya dinomore tse tharo e e neelwang mo tlhalosong ya pataganyotiragatso.
  • O ka bona bokana jo bo lefisitsweng kgotsa khoutu ya dinomore tsa 3 ka go tlhola seteitemente sa gago sa karatamolato. Go ikaegile ka Tirelo ya banka ya gago, seno se ka dirwa mo inthaneteng, ka mogala, kgotsa ka seteitemente sa pampiri se se tlang le imeile.
  • O tlhoka go feleletsa netefatso eno ka di {3}, mme o na le ditshono di le {4} tsa go leka gape.
  • Go ikaegile ka lefelo la gago le lefelo la banka e e neelanang ka karata ya gago, banka e ka nna ya lefisa Madi a Tuelo ya Bodit?habat?haba (ITF) kgotsa ya diragatsa ditefiso tsa phetolelo ya ledi go bokana jo bo lefisiwang ka nako ya tiragatso ya netefatso. Go tlhola gore a ditefiso tseo di ka dira, tsweetswee tlhola la banka e e neelanang ka karata. ITF kgotsa tefiso ya phetolelo ya ledi e e nnang teng mo tiragatsong ya netefatso ga e KITLA e busediwa madi ke Microsoft.
data.comment: PICVC DDPayin term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.value: Re kgobokanya Nomore ya Pabalesego ya Loago (SSN) ya gago go tswa mo go wena re bo re e tlhakanela le batho ba boraro ba ba porofešenale e le gore go diragadiwe go tlhola ga seemo sa melato go bona gore a o tshwanelegela thebolo. Re dirisa mekgwa ya botegeniki go thusa go sireletsa kgatlhanong le tetlelesego e e sa letlelelwang go, tiriso kgotsa go utulolwa ga di-SSN. Re fetisa SSN ka lefaratlhatlha le le babalesegileng le le sireletsegileng pele ga phetiso. Ga re boloke SSN morago ga go fetsa go tlholwa ga seemo sa melato, le fa gone re boloka setlhaodi se se kgethegileng se se ntshitsweng go tswa go SSN ya gago ka mabaka a ditaolo tsa kgapetsa. Gape re tla boloka maduo a melato le tshedimosetso e nngwe e re a bonang e le karolo ya go tlhola seemo sa melato ka lobaka lo lo tlhokegang ka mo go utlwalang go feleletsa pataganyotiragatso bakeng sa go lemoga le go thibela tshenyo.
data.comment: Info for SSN.

data.name: Literal.CreditCheck.ThingsToKnow

Go tlholwa ga seemo sa melato gono ga go a tshwanela go ama selekanyo sa gago sa seemo sa melato.

O ka dira diphetogo go tuelo ya gago le tshedimosetso ya tefiso mo nakong e e tlang ka go ya go https://live.xbox.com/en-US/account

data.name: Word.SEPA.TermConditions
data.value: Ka go dirisa taelo eno, o tlhophile Tebiti ya ka Tlhamalalo e le tsela ya gago ya tuelo. Go dirisa ga gago Tebiti ya ka Tlhamalalo go ikaegile ka gore a o amogela melawana eno le go dira tumalanong le yone. O naya Microsoft Payments Ltd. tetla ("re" kgotsa "rona") go kgopa tuelo go tswa go banka ya gago ya madi a a kolotiwang Microsoft. O tshwanetse wa tlhomamisa gore: (i) o neelane ka aterese ya imeile e e siameng malebana le go ikgolaganya le wena le dikitsiso; (ii) banka ya gago e tla amogela dikokoanyo tsa tebiti ya ka tlhamalalo; (iii) o na le madi a a lekaneng mo letlheng lepe fela la go duela; le (iv) gore taelo ya gago ga e a khanselwa (ntle le e e fa tlase) kgotsa ya gogelwa morago. Go palelwa ke go latela melawana eno go go dirang gore go se duelwe, ga go role morwalo maikarabelo a gago a go re duela madi ape fela a o re a kolotang. Tsweetswee ikgolaganye le rona fa o batla go khansela taelo eno kgotsa go tlhopha tsela e nngwe ya tuelo. Re tla khansela taelo ya gago fa re sena go amogela kitsiso ya gago. Tebiti ya ka Tlhamalalo e teng go ya kafa re tlhophang ka teng, mme ga e sa tlhole e le teng, re tla ikgolaganya le wena go rulaganya sengwe se sele.
data.comment: The content of "Term & Conditions" for SEPA.

Go dirisa ga gago Tebiti ya ka Tlhamalalo go ikaegile ka go amogela le go latela melawana eno. O letla Microsoft Online, Inc. ("rona" kgotsa "rotlhe") go kopa tuelo go tswa go banka ya gago ya madi a a kolotiwang Microsoft. O tshwanetse wa tlhomamisa gore: (i) o re neetse aterese ya imeile e e siameng ya go ikgolaganya le dikitsiso; (ii) banka ya gago e tla amogela kokoanyo ya tebiti ya ka tlhamalalo; (iii) o na le madi a a lekaneng mo letlheng lepe fela le go duelwang ka lone; le (iv) gore taelo ya gago ga ya khanselwa (ntle le jaaka fa tlase) kgotsa go busediwa morago. Go palelwa ke go latela melawana eno go go ka dirang gore go seka ga nna le tuelo, ga go reye gore o ka se tlhole o duela madi ape a o a kolotang kgotsa a a tshwanetseng go duelwa. Tsweetswee ikgolaganye le rona go khansela taelo eno kgotsa go tlhopha tsela e nngwe ya tuelo. Re tla khansela taelo ya gago fa re amogela kitsiso ya gago. Tebiti ya ka Tlhamalalo e teng go ya kafa re sweditseng ka teng, mme ga e se teng, re tla ikgolaganya le wena go rulaganya sengwe se sele.
data.comment: The term & conditions for Adcenter.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement
data.value: By checking this box, you authorize (A) Microsoft Payments Ltd. ("Microsoft") to send instructions to your bank to debit your account, and (B) your bank to debit your account in accordance with the instructions of Microsoft. As part of your rights, you are entitled to a refund from your bank under the terms and conditions of your agreement with your bank. A refund must be claimed within 8 weeks starting from the date on which your account was debited. Your rights are explained in a statement that you can obtain from your bank.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement.New
data.value: Fa o kwadisa kgotsa o tlhopha akhaonto ya gago ya banka gore e nne one mokgwa o o o dirisang go duela, o naya Microsoft (kgotsa moemedi wa yone) dithata tsa go goga madi gangwe kgotsa go feta a a lekanang dilo tse o di rekileng (go akaretsa le makgetho a a tshwanetseng go duelwa, dituelo le ditshenyegelo tsa go romela) kgotsa a peeletso (tumalanong le melao e e laolang peeletso ya gago) mo akhaontong ya gago ya banka (le gore, fa go tlhokega, e tsenye madi gangwe kgotsa go feta mo akhaontong ya gago ya banka go baakanya diphoso, e buse madi a a ntshitsweng kgotsa sengwe se se tshwanang le seo), e bile o naya setheo sa tsa madi se se tshwereng akhaonto ya gago ya banka go goga madi ao kgotsa go a amogela. O a tlhaloganya gore dithata tseno di tla nna di diragadiwa go fitlhela o tlosa tshedimosetso ya akhaonto ya gago ya banka mo akhaontong ya gago ya Microsoft kgotsa ya Skype.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement.MSfB
data.value: Fa o kwadisa akhaonto ya gago ya banka gore ke yone tsela ya gago ya go duela, o a bo o bontsha gore o a amogela gore ke akhaonto ya kgwebo e bile o naya Microsoft (kgotsa baemedi ba yone) dithata tsa go goga madi a selo se se dumeletsweng go rekwa. Ba tla tswelela ba dirisa dithata tseno go fitlha o phimola tshedimosetso ya akhaonto ya gago ya banka mo akhaontong ya gago ya Microsoft kgotsa mo akhaontong ya Skype.

data.name: Litterate.PayBitcoin.Description
data.value:
Tsweetswee tlhopha nngwe ya ditlhopho tsa go tsenya madi:
• Fa e le gore serweboleta sa sekgwama sa gago sa dijithale se tsentswe mo khomphiutheng ya gago, tobetsa konopo ya 'Duela ka Bitcoin'
• Fa e le gore sekgwama sa gago sa dijithale se bolokilwe mo smartphone ya gago, sekena khoutu ya QR

Tsweetswee duela madi a Bitcoin a lolame jaaka a tsopotswe fa tlase. O na le metsotso e le 15 go fetsa ka tuelo. Tsebe e tla itsosolosa ka go itirisa fa tuelo e se na go amogelwa.

data.name: Literal.Error.PolicyReject
data.value: Tshwarelo, ga re amogele dikarata tsa tuelelo-pele. Tsweetswee leka mofuta o mongwe wa tuelo.
data.comment: The error message for RIME_PrePaid_List_POLICY_REJECT from RISK team.

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsg
data.value: Dikhasetomara tes di dirisang dibatli tsa webo kwantle ga IE (Internet Explorer) ga di kitla di saenela ditirelo tse diša tsa Azure ka ntlha ya mathata a go tsenya ActiveX. Tsweetswee dirisa IE kgotsa VM (Virtual Machine) e e nang le IE gore o kgone go saenela go tsenwa. Morago ga go kwadisa mokgwatuelo, o tla kgona go dirisa dibatli tse dingwe tsa webo tsa ditirelo tsa Azure. Re kopa maitshwarelo go bo re go baketse matsapa .
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsgActiveX
data.value: E re ka tsela eno ya go duela e theilwe mo ActiveX, fa o dirisa dibatli tse dingwe (go akaretsa Microsoft Edge) mo boemong jwa Internet Explorer, o ka se kgone go tswelela o dirisa Azure. Tsweetswee dirisa Internet Explorer go ikwadisa. Fa o sena go ikwadisa, o ka nna wa dirisa sebatli sepe fela. Re maswabi ka bothata jono.
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Inicis.NameMsg
data.value: Tsweetswee tsenya leina la gago ka Seesemane gore le tlhage sentle mo dirasiting tsa gago.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.Header
data.value: Ntšhwafatsa dituelo tsa gago tse di dumeletsweng go sa le gale

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.SubHeader
data.value: Jaanong o ka kgona go dirisa tetla e o e ntshitseng go sa le gale ya go duela ya Microsoft gongwe le gongwe kwa PayPal e leng gone fa o duela mo Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.US
data.value: Dirisa PayPal fa o duela mo Microsoft mo nakong e e tlang. Fa o na le madi a a setseng mo PayPal, go tla dirisiwa madi ao pele, tota le fa o tlhophile mokgwa o mongwe o o o ratang wa go duela. Fa o sa tlhopha mokgwa o o o ratang wa go duela, go tla dirisiwa mokgwa o o o rulaganyeditseng ruri wa go duela. Fa mokgwa o o o ratang kgotsa o o o rulaganyeditseng ruri wa go duela o felelwa ke nako kgotsa o ganwa, PayPal e tla goga madi mo mokgwa-tlaleletsong wa go duela. O ka kgona go rulaganya kgotsa go fetola mokgwa wa gago wa go duela, kgotsa wa khansela tetla e o e ntshang nako nngwe le nngwe fela mo Diseting tsa gago mo Paypal.com. Go fitlhela o rulaganya mokgwa wa go duela mo Diseting tsa gago, mokgwa wa go duela o o dirisiwang e tla nna o o tsamaisanang le dipholisi tsa go duela tsa mo PayPal.com.
data.comment: Text for United States, Canada, Brazil

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.DE
data.value: O dumela gore Microsoft e ka nna ya fetisetsa ditaelo tsa gago tsa go duela mo PayPal, gore o kgone go duela ka tlhamalalo ka PayPal dilo tsa Microsoft mo Microsoft le batho ba bangwe ba ba itseweng ba ba amogelang dituelo ba dirisa Microsoft. O letla PayPal go naya Microsoft dintlha tsa gago tsa dituelo tsa PayPal go akaretsa le tshedimosetso e ka tlwaelo e newang yo o amogelang dituelo tlase ga Polisi ya rona ya Polokodiphiri. Seno se thusa Microsoft go bona fa tuelo ya gago e amogetswe e bile se thusa go wetsa tuelo e o e dirileng. PayPal e ka nna ya itsise Microsoft fa o gogela tumelelo ya gago morago. O laela PayPal go tsaya dikopo tsa dituelo tse di romelwang ke Microsoft e le tse o ntshitseng tetla ya tsone. Fa o na le madi a a setseng mo PayPal, go tla dirisiwa one pele. Fa karolo e o duelang ka yone ka gale e sa amogelwa kgotsa e feletswe ke nako, go tla gogwa madi mo akhaonto-tlaleletsong ya gago. O ka khansela taelo eno kgotsa wa fetola akhaonto e o duelang ka yone nako nngwe le nngwe mo akhaontong ya gago ya PayPal. Fa o duela ka mofuta wa madi o e seng one o o dirisiwang ke Akhaonto ya gago ya PayPal, PayPal e tla fetola madi ao e dirisa selekanyo se re se dirisang ka nako eo.
data.comment: Text for Germany, Netherlands, Sweden, United Kingdom, Russia

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText
data.value: Fa go tshwanelang gone, dikhasetomara tsa EU di tshwanetse go tsenya dintlha tsa dinomoro tsa tsone tsa kwadiso ya VAT. Fa ba sa dire jalo seno se ka nna sa ama tsela e VAT e tshwarang ka yone tshupamolato e e ntshitsweng ke Microsoft.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text

data.name: Literal.EG.OrgProfile.LegalText
data.value: Where applicable, Egypt customers should provide details of their valid VAT registration number. Failure to do so may impact upon the VAT treatment of the invoice issued by Microsoft.
data.comment: Egypt update organization profile legal text

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line1
data.value: Dilo le ditirelo tsa lekgetho tsa New Zealand (NZ GST) ka 15% di a dira mo ditirelong tse di dirwang ka kwa ntle ga melelwane le dilo tse dingwe tse di sa tshwaregeng tse o di newang ke batlamedi ba e seng baagi ba mo nageng ba tlamela baagi ba kwa New Zealand ntle le fa motho yoo e le kgwebo e e kwadisitsweng mo GST. Motlamedi o tshwanetse go tshwara moamogela ditirelo jaaka motho yo o sa kwadisiwang ntle le fa motho yono a itsise motlamedi gore o kwadisitswe e bile a bontsha nomoro ya gagwe ya kwadiso ya NZ GST.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line2
data.value: Mo ntlheng eno, re kopa o re neye nomoro ya kwadiso ya NZ GST ya setlamo sa gago. Go seng jalo, o ka nna wa duedisiwa 15% ya NZ GST mo dilong tse re go nayang tsone.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line3
data.value: Fa go nna le diphetogo dingwe mo nomorong ya kwadiso ya NZ GST ya setlamo sa gago kgotsa fa setlamo sa gago se ka phimola kwadiso ya sone ya GST kwa New Zealand, tsweetswee re itsise ka bonakonako.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.BR.Line1
data.value: Tsweetswee tsenya CNPJ fa e le gore o setlamo sa kgwebo/sa dilo tsa molao. Fa o sa tsenye CNPJ seno se raya gore ga o setlamo.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for Brazil

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.BR.Line2
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for Brazil

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.UnknownCountries
data.value: Otara eno e tlhoka gore go nne le tumelelo e nngwe ya gore o ka newa dilo ka sekoloto gore e kgone go duedisiwa ka tshupamolato. Tsweetswee tshwaya lebokoso leno gore o dumele go tlholwa gore a o ka newa dilo ka sekoloto. Go tla ikgolaganngwa le wena fa re batla tshedimosetso e nngwe. Otara eno e tla emisiwa go sekae go fitlhela go ntshiwa tumelelo mme ga go na go ntshiwa dilaesense dipe go fitlhela sekoloto se dumelelwa. Seno se ka nna sa tsaya go fitlha go dibeke di le pedi go diragadiwa. (Gape o ka nna wa fetola mekgwa ya go duela gore o tswelele ka otara eno.)
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for Unknown Countries

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Subheading
data.value: Ka go amogela ntšhwafatso eno, o tla kgona go dirisa akhaonto ya gago ya PayPal gongwe le gongwe kwa PayPal e leng gone ka Microsoft Pay.

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Text
data.value: O dumela go letla Microsoft go fetisetsa ditaelo tsa gago tsa tuelo ya PayPal go PayPal tsa dilo tse di rekilweng ka tlhamalalo mo Microsoft kgotsa moamogela tuelo yo o lemogilweng o dirisa dilo tsa Microsoft. Fa o na le madi a a setseng mo PayPal, go tla dirisiwa one pele. Fa mokgwa o o o ratang wa go duela kgotsa o o rulaganyeditsweng go sa le gale o sa amogelwa kgotsa o felelwa ke nako, go tla gogwa madi mo akhaontong-tlaleletsong ya gago. You allow PayPal to share your PayPal transaction details with Microsoft. Go naya ba bangwe dintlha tsa tuelo ya gago ya PayPal go thusa Microsoft go itse gore a tuelo ya gago e amogetswe kgotsa jang, go thusa go diragatsa tuelo ya gago le go ntsha dirasiti tsa tuelo jaaka fa di lemogwa mo Pholising ya PayPal. O laela PayPal go tshwara dikopo tsa tuelo tse di rometsweng ke Microsoft jaaka tse di dumeletsweng ke wena tumalanong le Tumalano ya Modirisi ya PayPal. Fa o duela ka madi a e seng madi a a dirisiwang ke Akhaonto ya gago ya PayPal, PayPal e tla fetola madi ao e dirisa madi a re tla bong re a dirisa ka nako eo. O ka kgona go khansela taelo eno kgotsa wa fetola mokgwa o o o ratang wa akhaonto nako nngwe le nngwe mo akhaontong ya gago ya PayPal. Fa o gogela morago tumelelo ya gago ya go dirisa PayPal mo Microsoft, PayPal e a nna ya itsise Microsoft.
data.comment: PayPal Scenario Strings - Agreement text for the update Paypal billing agreement page

data.value: Where is my CVV? The 4 digit code on the front.
data.comment: This is the hint for CVV amex textbox in xboxnative
